Package: dicom-oct%type_pkg[oct]
Version: 0.1.1
Type: oct (3.4.3 3.6.0 3.6.1), forge (dicom), gcc (4.7)
Revision: 2
Maintainer: Alexander Hansen <alexkhansen@users.sourceforge.net>
